<div>
  <h1>{{title}}</h1>
  <p>Welcome to <em>LocalLibrary</em>, a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer
  Network.</p>

  {{#if error}}
    Error getting dynamic content.
  {{ else }}
    The library has the following record counts:
 
   <ul>
     <li><span class="has-text-weight-semibold">Books:</span>{{data.book_count}}</li>
     <li><span class="has-text-weight-semibold">Copies:</span>{{data.book_instance_count}}</li>
     <li><span class="has-text-weight-semibold">Copies available:</span>{{data.book_instance_available_count}}</li>
     <li><span class="has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>{{data.author_count}}</li>
     <li><span class="has-text-weight-semibold">Genres:</span>{{data.genre_count}}</li> 
  </ul>
  {{/if}}

</div>
